  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Determine the magnetic flux through a surface, knowing the strength of the magnetic field, the surface area, and the angle between the normal to the surface and the magnetic field</item>
<item>Use Faraday&#8217;s law to determine the magnitude of induced emf in a closed loop due to changing magnetic flux through the loop</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:language>en</md:language>
